nodes.text: A city of towering buildings stood on the surface of the lush world of Tatooine in the year 25,793 BBY. It was home to some of the world's native Kumumgah. In that year, the forces of the Rakatan Infinite Empire invaded Tatooine and set fire to the city. The Kumumgah were rounded up as slaves, and the Force-sensitives among them were culled.
